work_summary: Bootstrap repo skeleton, templates, .codex audit trail, and issue #1 review
Create CI issue/ADR/runbook; add GitHub Actions workflows with Linux tests + self-hosted Xcode job; trigger CI and capture run URL
Fix CI workflows; enforce arm64 runner labels; ensure xcresult uploads even on failure; verify CI green + artifacts; prove runner via workflow_dispatch
Codex governance lock-in: document immutable prompt/follow-up rules and execution discipline in AGENTS.md
Create ingest CLI + deterministic staging manifest/layout with unit tests; docs runbook_ingest; verify CI green and artifacts
Create identity build CLI with name parsing/normalization; generate people.json + aliases.json from staging; add tests + runbook; verify CI green
Add deterministic de-id command producing share-safe dataset + mapping/manifest/layout; add synthetic CDA/FHIR tests; docs runbook_deid; verify CI green
Add pipeline run orchestrator with run_report.json; integration test for share mode end-to-end; docs runbook_pipeline; verify CI green

Implement `healthdelta export ndjson` from pipeline outputs (HealthKit XML + FHIR JSON + CDA) with deterministic, share-safe NDJSON streams; add synthetic tests + runbook_ndjson; update audit artifacts; verify tests locally
Create deterministic DuckDB loader/query CLI for canonical NDJSON streams; add schema + synthetic tests; update CI to install duckdb; add runbook_duckdb and audit artifacts; verify CI green

Add deterministic share-safe reporting CLI from DuckDB; generate summary.json/md and coverage/timeline CSV artifacts; synthetic DuckDB report tests; docs runbook_reports; audit artifacts; verify CI green

Add incremental run registry in state dir with deterministic input fingerprints + run_id derivation and no-op when unchanged; add run register command; update pipeline CLI with --state/--since; add synthetic tests and runbook_incremental; audit artifacts; verify CI green

Implement `healthdelta run all` operator command (share-safe default) to orchestrate pipeline -> NDJSON -> DuckDB -> reports with deterministic no-op; add synthetic integration test and runbook_operator; update audit artifacts
Implement `healthdelta note build` to produce deterministic share-safe doctor_note.txt/md from DuckDB; add synthetic DuckDB-backed tests, runbook_note, and audit artifacts

Integrate Doctor’s Note into `healthdelta run all` (direct function call) with deterministic note paths and registry pointers; add ADR_3 and update runbook_operator + tests; prepare CI evidence and issue comments

Add `healthdelta export profile` to generate deterministic, share-safe export directory profiling artifacts (files/ext counts, HealthKit Record types, sampled FHIR resourceTypes, CDA tag counts) with synthetic fixtures, tests, and runbook_profile
Add share-safe in-repo living plan/backlog and local issue artifact template; create backlog issues #17–#22; update AGENTS.md; add audit artifacts; verify CI proof and close

Add canonical export layout resolver and update `export profile` to use it; add wrapped-layout fixtures/tests ensuring deterministic, share-safe outputs and exclusion of unrelated files; audit artifacts and CI closure

Update ingest to use export layout resolver, stage export_cda.xml, and restrict clinical JSON staging to the clinical records tree only; update tests for CDA presence and exclusion of unrelated JSON; add audit artifacts and close with CI proof
Remove redundant CDA staging logic from pipeline/operator and rely on ingest staging/layout; strengthen pipeline/operator tests to prove CDA propagates through share mode; close with CI proof

Add deterministic `healthdelta export validate` for NDJSON streams (newline-delimited JSON objects, required keys, optional banned token/pattern checks) with synthetic tests and runbook; close with CI proof

Add deterministic `healthdelta share bundle` to package share-safe run artifacts (deid/ndjson/duckdb/reports/note + registry snippet) into a byte-stable tar.gz; synthetic tests ensure staging/identity excluded and banned tokens absent; close with CI proof
